# Project Rules

Project-specific rules that supplement (and may override) the framework's
`rules/` directory. Copy this template to `rules/project.md` in your
project (or a subdirectory) and edit.

The framework's `rules/OVERVIEW.md` auto-loads:
- `rules/contributing.md`
- `rules/public-repo.md`
- `rules/memory-discipline.md`
- `rules/multi-agent-worktree.md`
- `rules/external-plugin-policy.md`
- `rules/policy/security-guards.md`

So you only need to write what *differs*.

